name: Anomaly - 051
description: Hot to the touch, this is another anomaly that has landed on earth from the far reaches of space, we're not sure where from exactly. It has several eyes and a formless, constantly shifting shape. It's size can range from that of an ant, to the size of a male adults hand, seemingly able to shift at will. Highly aggressive, if others emerge, do not attempt to contain in anything other than composite 7-63. It has a huge appetite for inorganic materials.
